title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: A surprising lack of support from a friend or group throws you for a loop today. Unfortunately, striking back in anger wont get you what you want. Instead, direct your energy more toward solving your problem rather than believing the perfect solution lies in the hands of others. It might not be optimal that you must rely on your own wits and resources now. However, discovering more about your natural ability to handle a crisis builds your confidence. The bumpiest roads can lead to the most beautiful destinations. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
